Bangladesh never looked like chasing down the total as they lost wickets at crucial intervals. India ended a superb ODI series with a sizzling 227 run victory.

snippet.title: Officer Purvi Becomes Hostage Of A Strange Criminal | CID | Strange Crimes | सीआईडी | Full Episode
snippet.description:
Former crime branch officer Ketan makes a video call to show Abhijeet his new farmhouse. Suddenly Ketan gets stabbed and dies. Meanwhile, the CID team finds another body in an unidentified state of crime branch officer Maheen. Abhijeet shares his experience working a case with Ketan, Meehan, and Purvi four years ago. Is there any connection between the old case and the crime? What is it? Watch the full episode now! 

Show Name: CID 
Show Cast & Characters: 
• Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
• Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy
• Ashutosh Gowariker as Sr. Inspector Virendra
• Dayanand Shetty as Sr. Inspector Daya
• Narendra Gupta as Dr. R. P. Salunkhe
• Aditya Srivastava as Sr. Inspector Abhijeet
• Shraddha Musale as Dr. Tarika
• Ansha Sayed as Sub-Inspector Purvi
Episode No: 1465
Producer: Brijendra Pal Singh

#CID #सीआईडी #CID2022 #CrimeThrillers #CrimeMysteries #Mysteries #Horror #LIVCrime #NewCID #Crime

Click here to Subscribe to LIV Crime: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCzXpAx4v6rFLYXkJZ5nmSvQ?sub_confirmation=1

About CID: 
----------------- 
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

Click here to watch all the episodes of CID Unusual Investigations: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL0y08jtgaKIU34U5_3uGi2Slf8jma4JLs

snippet.title: उसके बाद 'पापा और भाई से भी घिन आती है' | Sushma Yadav | Josh Talks Hindi
snippet.description:
Sushma जी तो उस बंद कमरें से बाहर निकल आयी 
लेकिन अब आपकी बारी हैं, उस बंद कमरे बाहर निकलने की 
और आपने सपनों को पूरा करने की : https://joshskills.app.link/gTdpJwrDDvb

Sushma Yadav is from a small village in Haryana. Sushma Yadav was married at the young age of 12 years. She wanted to become an IPS or Police officer by being well educated since childhood. Even after marriage, she did not give up her desire to study and fought vigorously for her rights in society. Sushma Yadav is doing a respectable job in Haryana as a Policewoman today after facing all life's challenges & difficulties.
Today she will tell her story through Josh Talks. So do watch this women's motivational/inspirational video of Josh Talks completely.

Sushma Yadav Haryana के एक छोटे से गाँव से हैं. Sushma Yadav की शादी 12 साल की छोटी सी उम्र में कर दी गई थी. इन्हे बचपन से ही पढ़ लिख कर IPS या Police officer बनना था. शादी के बाद भी इन्होंने अपनी पढ़ने की चाहत को नहीं छोड़ा और समाज से अपने हक के लिए डट कर लड़ी. Sushma Yadav आज ज़िंदगी के सभी Challenges का सामना करके Haryana Police में एक सम्मानजनक नौकरी कर रही हैं.
आज जोश Talks के माध्यम से ये बताएंगी अपनी कहानी. तो जोश Talks की इस women motivational/inspirational video को पूरा ज़रूर देखें. 

#JoshTalksHindi #SushmaYadavJoshTalks #womenmotivation 

Josh Talks Hindi aims to inspire and motivate you by bringing to you the best Hindi motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 7 regional languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the challenges they face in their careers or business and helping them discover their true calling in life. 

“ज़िंदगी में कुछ बड़ा करने के लिए जोश का होना बहुत ज़रूरी है.” 
इसी सोच के साथ एक शुरुआत हुई. देश के कोने-कोने से सबसे प्रेरणादायक कहानियों को चुनकर हर उस शख्स तक पहुंचाने की जो बड़े सपने देखता है. 
इसी सोच का नाम है जोश Talks. 
वो मंच जहां कई Role Models आते हैं और अपने जीवन की प्रेरणादायक कहानी हमारे साथ शेयर करते हैं. वो अपने जीवन के उन किस्सों को शेयर करते हैं जहां वो Fail हुए, उन्होंने गलतियां की, कई बार हिम्मत भी टूटी पर अपने लक्ष्य को हासिल करके ही माने. 

अगर दो शब्दों में कहा जाए, तो जोश Talks हम सबके लिए हमारे ‘बड़े भैय्या/बड़ी बहन’ की तरह है. 
जो हमेशा हमारे दोस्त बनकर हमारी बात सुनते हैं और हमें कुछ नया सिखाते हैं.
तो चलो, जोश के साथ हर Goal को हासिल करें. :)

और हां! अगर हमारे पास ऐसे लोगों की कहानियां हैं जिन्होंने अपनी मेहनत और हिम्मत के दम पर अच्छा मुकाम हासिल किया है. जिससे आज वो समाज के लिए एक Role Model बन गए हैं. 
तो, अभी लिखकर भेज देते हैं - speakers@joshtalks.com

► जोश Talks Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/JoshTalksHindi​ 
► जोश Talks Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/JoshTalksHi... 

-----**DISCLAIMER**----- 
All of the views and work outside the pretext of the video of the speaker, are his/ her own, and Josh Talks, by any means, does not support them directly or indirectly and neither is it liable for it. Viewers are requested to use their own discretion while viewing the content and focus on the entirety of the story rather than finding inferences in its parts. Josh Talks by any means, does not further or amplify any specific ideology or propaganda.

आज जोश Talks के माध्यम से ये बताएंगी अपनी कहानी. तो जोश Talks की इस women motivational/inspirational video को पूरा ज़रूर देखें. 

#JoshTalksHindi #SushmaYadavJoshTalks #womenmotivation 

Josh Talks Hindi aims to inspire and motivate you by bringing to you the best Hindi motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 7 regional languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the challenges they face in their careers or business and helping them discover their true calling in life. 

“ज़िंदगी में कुछ बड़ा करने के लिए जोश का होना बहुत ज़रूरी है.” 
इसी सोच के साथ एक शुरुआत हुई. देश के कोने-कोने से सबसे प्रेरणादायक कहानियों को चुनकर हर उस शख्स तक पहुंचाने की जो बड़े सपने देखता है. 
इसी सोच का नाम है जोश Talks. 
वो मंच जहां कई Role Models आते हैं और अपने जीवन की प्रेरणादायक कहानी हमारे साथ शेयर करते हैं. वो अपने जीवन के उन किस्सों को शेयर करते हैं जहां वो Fail हुए, उन्होंने गलतियां की, कई बार हिम्मत भी टूटी पर अपने लक्ष्य को हासिल करके ही माने. 

अगर दो शब्दों में कहा जाए, तो जोश Talks हम सबके लिए हमारे ‘बड़े भैय्या/बड़ी बहन’ की तरह है. 
जो हमेशा हमारे दोस्त बनकर हमारी बात सुनते हैं और हमें कुछ नया सिखाते हैं.
तो चलो, जोश के साथ हर Goal को हासिल करें. :)

और हां! अगर हमारे पास ऐसे लोगों की कहानियां हैं जिन्होंने अपनी मेहनत और हिम्मत के दम पर अच्छा मुकाम हासिल किया है. जिससे आज वो समाज के लिए एक Role Model बन गए हैं. 
तो, अभी लिखकर भेज देते हैं - speakers@joshtalks.com

snippet.title: Filmymoji || Middle Class Madhu || Amma Aligithey || MCM
snippet.description:
Filmymoji || Middle Class Madhu || Amma Aligithey || MCM

In this new Middle Class Madhu episode, the video opens with the game we all used to play as kids, Allilu Aata (Game With Marbles). Our Naatu Guntalu Gang returns home after enjoying a good time. Madhu returns home and discovers no food, which makes him angry with his mother. In the meantime, after a busy day at work Madhus' father arrives home and discovers no excellent food, which makes him angry with his wife. Even though Madhu's mother does all the housework to the best of her ability, she feels horrible because of Madhu and his husband. For an entertaining twenty minute journey, watch the complete video of this Amma Aligithey episode, "What if mom gets angry?"

snippet.title: PM Narendra Modi Marathi Speech | Samruddhi Mahamarg Inauguration | मोदींचे नागपुरात भाषण
snippet.description:
The 521 km Nagpur-Shirdi highway in the first phase of the Hindu Heart Emperor Balasaheb Thackeray Prosperity Highway was inaugurated by Prime Minister Modi today. On this occasion, Modi made a speech in Nagpur.

हिंदुहृदयसम्राट बाळासाहेब ठाकरे समृद्धी महामार्गाच्या पहिल्या टप्प्यातील नागपूर-शिर्डी या 521 किमी महामार्गाचं पंतप्रधान मोदींच्या हस्ते आज लोकार्पण करण्यात आले. यावेळी नागपुरात मोदींनी भाषण केलं.  

n18oc_maharashtra


#Modispeech #samruddhimahamarg #pmmodi #nagpur   #maharashtrapolitics  #news18lokmat #marathinews #lokmat #live 



News18 India’s leading News Network, and the Lokmat Group, Maharashtra’s leading Newspaper group, present News18Lokmat (formerly- IBN-Lokmat ) - a 24-hour Marathi News and Current Affairs Channel. The legacy of these two renowned media powerhouses will give News18Lokmat a sense of immense credibility as well as access to a vast audience base. Going on air from April 6, News18Lokmat will be a world-class credible News channel for the highly aware and conscious ‘Progressive Marathi’.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3638 - 10 Dec 2022 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3637: Bhide Ka Gussa
--------------------------------------------------------
Bhide is at Popatlal's door with the intention to catch Popatlal and teach him a lesson for the stunt he pulled. But the door is locked and Popatlal is inside, hiding. Bhide brings a stick and he is going to break down the door when Madhavi and Sonu try to calm him down and make him understand. But Bhide is too angry for explanations. When Bhide fails to open the door, he goes to Iyer's place to ask for a spare key. Popatlal, upon hearing this decides to take extreme steps in escaping Bhide. he rushes to the balcony and plans to make an escape.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3638, 10 Dec 2022
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: Pushpa Pushpa - Vedha | Dr. Shivrajkumar | A Harsha | Zee Studios | Geetha Pictures
snippet.description:
Zee Studios and Geetha Pictures present the second single ‘Pushpa Pushpa’, sung by Karunaada Chakravarthy Dr. Shivarajkumar.
Pushpa Pushpa is the second single of Dr.ShivarajKumar's 125th film VEDHA. The title is directed by A Harsha. Arjun Janya has composed music, and this marks the 4th outing of the Actor-Director-Music director combination. 

Written and Directed by A. Harsha
Produced by Geetha Shivrajkumar & Zee Studios

snippet.title: Chandrakant Patil | शाईफेक करणाऱ्यांचे समर्थक आक्रमक, पिंपरी चिंचवड पोलीस ठाण्यासमोर केलं आंदोलन
snippet.description:
Chandrakant Patil had made a controversial statement on Friday. Why depend on government subsidy to start a school? Asking this, Chandrakant Patil said 'Mahatma Phule, Dr. Babasaheb Ambedkar, Karmaveer Bhaurao Patil had begged to start the school. Now the atmosphere has warmed up. Today in Pimpri Chinchwad, ink was thrown on Chandrakant Patil. The attackers have been detained by the police.   

चंद्रकांत पाटील यांनी शुक्रवारी वादग्रस्त वक्तव्य केलं होतं. शाळा सुरू करण्याकरता सरकारच्या अनुदानावर अवलंबून का राहता? असा सवाल करत चंद्रकांत पाटील यांनी 'महात्मा फुले, डॉ. बाबासाहेब आंबेडकर, कर्मवीर भाऊराव पाटील यांनी शाळा सुरू करण्यासाठी भीक मागितली होती,' असं वक्तव्य केलं आहे. यावरून आता वातावरण चांगलचं तापलं आहे. आज पिंपरी चिंचवडमध्ये चंद्रकांत पाटील यांच्यावर शाईफेक करण्यात आली आहे. हल्लेखोरांना पोलिसांनी ताब्यात घेतलं आहे.

चंद्रकांत पाटील यांनी शुक्रवारी वादग्रस्त वक्तव्य केलं होतं. शाळा सुरू करण्याकरता सरकारच्या अनुदानावर अवलंबून का राहता? असा सवाल करत चंद्रकांत पाटील यांनी 'महात्मा फुले, डॉ. बाबासाहेब आंबेडकर, कर्मवीर भाऊराव पाटील यांनी शाळा सुरू करण्यासाठी भीक मागितली होती,' असं वक्तव्य केलं आहे. यावरून आता वातावरण चांगलचं तापलं आहे. आज पिंपरी चिंचवडमध्ये चंद्रकांत पाटील यांच्यावर शाईफेक करण्यात आली आहे. हल्लेखोरांना पोलिसांनी ताब्यात घेतलं आहे.

snippet.description:
#HimachalElectionResult    #reenakashyap     #LiveHindustan

Himachal Election में कांग्रेस पार्टी ने 40 सीटों के साथ बहुमत का आंकड़ा पार कर लिया है. इस बार चुनाव में कई ऐसे रिकॉर्ड बने जिसकी उम्मीद नहीं थी. चलिए आपको एक ऐसे ही हटकर खबर दिखाते है. और वो खबर है कि इस बार एक मात्र महिला विधायक विधानसभा पहुंची है. आखिर कौन. आपके मन में ये सवाल आ रहा होगा. तो चलिए बताते है. 68 सदस्यीय हिमाचल विधानसभा में पहुंचने वाली एकमात्र महिला विधायक कौन हैं..

snippet.title: PM Modi's speech at launch of various development works in Nagpur, Maharashtra
snippet.description:
Prime Minister Narendra Modi launches various development works in Nagpur, Maharashtra.

The Prime Minister, Shri Narendra Modi laid the foundation stone and dedicated to the nation various projects worth more than 75,000 crores in Maharashtra today. It includes national rail projects worth more than 1500 crores, National Institute of One Health (NIO), Nagpur and Nag river pollution abatement project, Nagpur. During the programme, the Prime Minister also dedicated ‘Central Institute of Petrochemicals Engineering & Technology (CIPET), Chandrapur’ to the nation and inaugurated ‘Centre for Research, Management and Control of Hemoglobinopathies, Chandrapur’.

snippet.title: White Brown Black - Avvy Sra | Karan Aujla | Jaani | Arvindr Khaira | Desi Melodies
snippet.description:
The most awaited collaboration of the year is finally here, Avvy Sra and Karan Aujla join hands to deliver ‘White Brown Black.' Everything about this song is the gold standard from Karan’s ace rap to Jaani’s unforgettable writing and Avvy’s impeccable music production. ‘White Brown Black’ goes hard with its modern sound design combined with folk elements; making it an absolute banger. The music video directed by Amaninder Singh from Arvindr Khaira’s team is everything you needed to complement Avvy and Karan’s fire vocals.

Listen to 'White Brown Black' on your favourite streaming platform - UMGI.lnk.to/WBB

snippet.title: Match Highlights - England 1:2 France - FIFA World Cup Qatar 2022 | JioCinema & Sports18
snippet.description:
Holders France booked their place in the semi-finals after beating England 2-1 at the Al Bayt Stadium.

The defending champions struck first through Aurelien Tchouameni, who fired in a belter from 25 yards out. England upped the ante in the second half and Harry Kane equalised from the spot after Bukayo Saka was hauled down by France's goalscorer.

Didier Deschamps' side upped the pressure & reclaimed the lead through Olivier Giroud in the 78th minute. That joy was going to be short-lived as England were awarded another penalty; only for Kane to sky his effort this time.

snippet.title: Match Highlights - Morocco 1:0 Portugal - FIFA World Cup Qatar 2022 | JioCinema & Sports18
snippet.description:
Pulling off yet another upset, Morocco ended Cristiano Ronaldo and Portugal's run at #Qatar2022 by the barest of margins. 

Coming into this high-octane quarter-final clash after defeating Spain in the Round of 16, the North African nation looked to create history. And they did, courtesy of Youssef En-Nesyri's 42nd-minute strike. Fernando Santos' men came close to finding an equaliser several times, but Moroccan goalkeeper Bono starred for his team once again.      

With this historic win, Morocco became the first African team to reach the semi-finals of #FIFAWorldCup. 

Relive the best moments from #MARPOR and keep watching the #WorldsGreatestShow LIVE on #JioCinema & #Sports18 📺📲

snippet.title: Match Highlights - Portugal 6:1 Switzerland - FIFA World Cup Qatar 2022 | JioCinema & Sports18
snippet.description:
No Cristiano Ronaldo, no problem as Portugal crushed Switzerland 6-1 to reach the #FIFAWorldCup quarter-finals for the first time since 2006.

Goncalo Ramos was the star performer in #PORSUI as he netted a sensational hat-trick; the first of #Qatar2022. Pepe & Raphael Guerreiro also got their names on the scoresheet in between the Benfica striker's goals. Substitute Rafael Leao added the cherry on top of the icing with a sublime finish in injury time.

Manuel Akanji bagged the consolation for Switzerland.

Enjoy the highlights of this clash & remember to watch Portugal in action again on Dec 10 - 8:30 pm, LIVE on #JioCinema & #Sports18 📺📲

#WorldsGreatestShow #FIFAWConJioCinema #FIFAWConSports18 #ShortsFIFAWorldCup

snippet.title: Decorating Home for Christmas in Tamil | Christmas Shopping Vlog in Tamil
snippet.description:
In this video join me during the christmas shopping and decorating the home during the festival season. It is always fun to decorate the home during christmas and putting up the christmas tree. I had also collected a lot of ornaments during the new years and its always bring joy to put them up. We also decorated the yard with some holiday lights and candy canes. We  also visited a couple of shops to take a look at the new decorations this year.
#christmasdecorations #christmasdecor #christmasvlog 

Friends, I hope you liked this week's vlog. See you next week with more interesting videos.

snippet.title: Siyani Episode 118 - [Eng Sub] - Anmol Baloch - Mohsin Abbas Haider -Saniya Shamshad - 10th Dec 2022
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Siyani Episode 118 - [Eng Sub] - Anmol Baloch - Mohsin Abbas Haider -Saniya Shamshad - 10th December 2022

Hailing from a lower-middle-class family, Kiran is a selfish and arrogant girl who aspires to achieve a lifestyle through mending her ways and taking shortcuts. Kiran’s mother Nusrat Ara is aware of her daughter’s nature and doesn’t stop her from doing anything. On the contrary, Ujala is a well-mannered and beautiful girl who lives with Kiran’s family and strives to become independent. 

Zarbab, a handsome young man who belongs to an influential and wealthy family. His first meeting with Kiran turns out to be magical as he falls in love at first sight. Kiran sees him as a way to advance forward in life and builds a web of lies and deceit around Zarbab. On the other hand, Ujala is forced to live a life deprived of love and unfulfilled dreams.

Will Ujala ever find the love and respect that she deserves? After building her life on lies and deception, how long will Kiran be able to conceal the truth?

Written By: Sadia Akhtar
Directed By: Ali Akbar
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

snippet.title: The Search For Coconuts Begins | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Watch the best moment from your beloved show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah where are characters are here to take you on a joyous ride. Get on the happy train and enjoy how these characters navigate through their daily lives in a hilarious way! Jethalal, Taarak, and all of the members eagerly await you.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 1393
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा  #SonyPAL

Subscribe to Sony Pal: http:/a/www.youtube.com/sonypalindia

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G0GGKekdfESeKWx2JOF9NFL

snippet.title: श्री कृष्ण लीला | श्री कृष्ण ने अश्वत्थामा को दिया था श्राप
snippet.description:
भक्त को भगवान से और जिज्ञासु को ज्ञान से जोड़ने वाला एक अनोखा अनुभव। तिलक प्रस्तुत करते हैं दिव्य भूमि भारत के प्रसिद्ध धार्मिक स्थानों के अलौकिक दर्शन। दिव्य स्थलों की तीर्थ यात्रा और संपूर्ण भागवत दर्शन का आनंद। 

Watch the video song of ''Darshan Do Bhagwaan'' here - https://youtu.be/j7EQePGkak0

Watch the story of "Shree krshn ne ashvatthaama ko diya tha shraap" now!

Watch Janmashtami Special Krishna Bhajan - Govind Madhav Jai Jai Gopal by Dev Negi - http://bit.ly/GovindMadhavJaiJaiGopal

अश्वत्थामा ब्रह्मषिर अस्त्र को पांडवों पर छोड़ देता है। श्री कृष्ण अर्जुन को कहते हैं की तुम भी अपने ब्रह्मषिर अस्त्र का प्रयोग कर अश्वत्थामा के अस्त्र को रोकने के लिए कहते हैं। अर्जुन भी अपने ब्रह्मषिर अस्त्र को चला देता है। वेदव्यास जी दोनों अस्त्रों के बीच में आकर उन्हें आपस में टकराने से रोक देते हैं और दोनों को अपना अस्त्र वापस ले लेने के लिए कहते हैं अर्जुन उनकी बात मान कर अपना अस्त्र वापस ले लेता है। लेकिन जब अश्वत्थामा उन्हें कहता है की मैं इस अस्त्र को वापस लेने की विद्या नहीं जानता। वेदव्यास जी अश्वत्थामा को कहते हैं की तुम इसे यदि वापस नहीं ले सकते तो तुम इसे पृथ्वी के उस हिस्से पर मोड़ दो जहां कोई भी जीव नहीं है और इसके बदले में तुम्हें पांडवों से अभय दान दिलवाता हूँ। श्री कृष्ण पांडवों से अश्वत्थामा को अभ्यदान देने के बदले उसकी दिव्य मणि को माँगते हैं जो की उसे सिर के भीतर थी जिस से उसे ना कभी भूक लगती थी और वह राज मुक्त रहता था। अश्वत्थामा अपने ब्रह्मषिर अभिमनयु की पत्नी उत्तरा के गर्भ की ओर मोड़ देता है। श्री कृष्ण उत्तरा के गर्भ की रक्षा करने के लिए अपने सुदर्शन चक्र को भेजते हैं। श्री कृष्ण ब्रह्मा जी से कहते हैं की आप अपने अस्त्र को वापस ले लें क्योंकि अश्वत्थामा ने इसका प्रयोग ग़लत कार्य के लिए किया है। ब्रह्मा जी अपने अस्त्र को वापस ले लेते हैं। श्री कृष्ण अश्वत्थामा को अपने कर्म के कारण श्राप देते हैं की तुम हज़ारों वर्षों के लिए इसी कल में जीवित रहोगे तुम्हें मृत्युु नहीं आएगी और तुमसे कोई भी इंसान बात नहीं करेगा और तुम्हारा शरीर ऐसा हो जाएगा की तुम स्वयं अपनी शक्ल को देख कर भी डर जाओगे। श्री कृष्ण भीम को अश्वत्थामा की दिव्य मणि निकल कर लाने के लिए कहते हैं। भीम उस मणि को उसके सर से निकल लेता है।

श्री कृष्ण के सभी एपिसोड और भजन देखने के लिए Subscribe करें तिलक YouTube चैनल को। 

Subscribe to Tilak for more devotional contents - https://bit.ly/SubscribeTilak

श्रीकृष्णा, रामानंद सागर द्वारा निर्देशित एक भारतीय टेलीविजन धारावाहिक है। मूल रूप से इस श्रृंखला का दूरदर्शन पर साप्ताहिक प्रसारण किया जाता था। यह धारावाहिक कृष्ण के जीवन से सम्बंधित कहानियों पर आधारित है। गर्ग संहिता , पद्म पुराण , ब्रह्मवैवर्त पुराण अग्नि पुराण, हरिवंश पुराण , महाभारत , भागवत पुराण , भगवद्गीता आदि पर बना धारावाहिक है सीरियल की पटकथा, स्क्रिप्ट एवं काव्य में बड़ौदा के महाराजा सयाजीराव विश्वविद्यालय के हिन्दी विभाग के अध्यक्ष डॉ विष्णु विराट जी ने महत्वपूर्ण भूमिका निभाई। इसे सर्वप्रथम दूरदर्शन के मेट्रो चैनल पर प्रसारित 1993 को किया गया था जो 1996 तक चला, 221 एपिसोड का यह धारावाहिक बाद में दूरदर्शन के डीडी नेशनल पर टेलीकास्ट हुआ, रामायण व महाभारत के बाद इसने टी आर पी के मामले में इसने दोनों धारावाहिकों को पीछे छोड़ दिया था,इसका पुनः जनता की मांग पर प्रसारण कोरोना महामारी 2020 में लॉकडाउन के दौरान रामायण श्रृंखला समाप्त होने के बाद ०३ मई से डीडी नेशनल पर किया जा रहा है, TRP के मामले में २१ वें हफ्ते तक यह सीरियल नम्बर १ पर कायम रहा।

snippet.title: Thee Thalapathy | Thalapathy Vijay | Varisu | STR | Vamshi Paidipally | Thaman
snippet.description:
Here is the most awaited second single "Thee Thalapathy" lyric video of Thalapathy Vijay’s #Varisu. 

Film Credits: 

Director: Vamshi Paidipally Producer: Raju, Shirish 
Banner: Sri Venkateswara Creations 
Co:Producers: Sri Harshith Reddy, Sri Harshitha Composed by Thaman S 

Star Cast: Vijay, Rashmika Mandanna, R Sarathkumar, Prabhu, Prakash Raj, Shaam, Srikanth, Khushbu, Yogi Babu, Jayasudha, Sangeetha Krish, Samyuktha Shanmughanathan, Nandini Rai, Ganesh Venkatraman, Sriman, VT Ganesan, John Vijay, Bharath Reddy, Sanjana and others. 

Story-Screenplay: Vamshi Paidipally, Hari & Ahishor Solomon Dialogues, Additional Screenplay, Lyrics: Vivek
Dop: Karthik Palani Editor: Praveen KL 
Production Design: Sunil Babu & Vaishnavi Reddy 
VFX: Yugandhar 
Action: Ram Laxman, Peter Hein & Dhilip Subbarayan Choreographer: Jani Master 
Costume Designers: Deepali Noor, Akangshee Chopra (Rashmika Mandanna) Co:Director: Rambabu Kongarapi 
Makeup: P Nagarajan 
Pro: Riaz K Ahmed 
Publicity Design: Gopi Prasannaa Stills: D Maneksha 
Production Controller: Kishore Surapaneni & KTS Swaminathan 
Executive Producer: B Sreedhar Rao & R Udhayakumar Associate Editor: M Sandeep 
Associate Cinematographer: Lokesh Ilayaa Second camera operator: N V Reddy 
Assistant Cinematographers: Sarath Krishna. R, Yadhavan Subramaniam, Thiyagu G, Sandeep Bapatla & Vivian Pullan 

Lyrical Video Credits: 
Visualised & Shot by: GK Vishnu 
Choreographer: Sandy 
Art Director: K Udayakumar 
Editor: R Kaliavanan 
Action: Dinesh Subbarayan 
Costume Designer: Pallavi Singh, Kavitha 

Song Credits: 

Song Title: Thee Thalapathy Album/Movie: Varisu 
Singer: STR (Silambarasan) 
Programmed & Arranged By Thaman S 
Lyrics: Vivek 

Musician Credits: 
Arranged & Programmed by Thaman S 
Live Lead Drums: Thaman S 
Additional Percussion & Timbale: Anandan Sivamani 
Electric Guitar: Godfrey 
28ORCHESTRA 
Record at 
STUDIO28 BANGKOK 
Studio Manager: Supisa Williamson 
Recording Engineer: THITIKORN ROYMANEE & SUTTHIPAT KUNAKORN 
Orchestra Manager: Thitanon Kollasathsenee 
HORN: Thanapak Poonpol Kotchakorn Samphalang Khanin Phruekpiti & Supreeti Ansvananda 
Tuba:Teerapat Decha 
Trumpet: Surasi Chanoksakul,Somjate,Pookaew,Supawanchai 
Trombone: Suttipong Mainaikij,Pradch Limvoranant 
Orchestra Co:Ordinator: Andrew T Mackay 
Vocal Supervision: Sri Krishna 
Additional Male vocals: Rahul Nambiar & Deepak blue 
Additions Female vocals by: Harika Narayan 
Harmony: Narayanan Ravishankar Sri Krishna 
Prudhvi Chandra & Saicharan 
Recording Engineers: Osho V 
Recorded @ V studio ( chennai )& Prasad film labs( Hyderabad ) 
Mixed & Mastered: Shadab Rayeen 
New edge ( Mumbai ) & New Edge ( NY ) 
Assistant by Pukraj & Anup 
Musician coordinator: Manikandan K 
Studio Manger: Seenu & Sridhar 
Studio Assistance: Kannan Lingam Raju & Ranjith 


Lyrics: 
Unna paathu sirichaa 
Adha ullukkulla nerupaakku 
Avamaanam kedachaa 
adhil greedam onna uruvaakku 
Unna kuththi ulagame 
aanandham adayume 
Thiruppi adikkum bodhu dhaan yaaru neennu puriyume 
Its time its time to give it:u back:u maame 
Idhu thiruppi idhu thiruppi kudukkum neram maame 
Udanja megame maa mazhaya kudukkume 
Kizhinja vedhayile thaan kaadu porakkume 
Pudhiya edhiriye vaa ennai edhirkave 
Pazhaya edhirigal en rasigar padayile 
Thee idhu Thalapathee 
Pera kettaa whistle adi 
Thee idhu Thalapathee 
Unga nenjin adhipathi 
Stanza 
Kaayam poruthu Sendru pazhagu mul irukkum vazhiyile 
Kooda nadandha kootta satham pullarikkum udalile 
Kaalgal thadukki malayil irundhu keezhe pogum nodiyile 
Kaigal asaithu paaru pudhiya rekkai pirakkum vazhiyile 
Kanneero 
Nee unakku sollum aaraaro 
Kan thoongi ezhundha pinbu nee vero 
Udanja megame maa mazhaya kudukkume 
Kizhinja vedhayile thaan kaadu porakkume 
Pudhiya edhiriye vaa ennai edhirkave 
Pazhaya edhirigal en rasigar padayile 
Thee idhu Thalapathee 
Pera kettaa whistle adi 
Thee idhu Thalapathee 
Unga nenjin adhipathi

___________________________________

snippet.title: Isudan Gadhvi એ ખંભાળિયાથી હાર બાદ પોતાના રાજકીય ભવિષ્ય વિશે શું કહ્યું? Gujarat Election 2022
snippet.description:
#aapgujarat #isudangadhvi #gujaratelection2022 #gujaratinews #gujaratelectionresult 

ગુજરાત વિધાનસભા ચૂંટણીમાં આમ આદમી પાર્ટીના મુખ્ય મંત્રીપદના ચહેરા ઈસુદાન ગઢવી ખંભાળિયાની બેઠક પરથી ચૂંટણી હારી ગયા છે. હાર બાદ અમે તેમની પ્રતિક્રિયા જાણવા તેમની સાથે વાતચીત કરી અને આગળ તેમની રાજનૈતિક દિશા શું રહેશે તેઓ  તેમના મતવિસ્તાર અને પક્ષ માટે કયા કાર્યોનું લક્ષ્ય રાખે છે એ જાણવાનો પ્રયાસ કર્યો.
તેમની સાથે વાતચીત કરી બીબીસી સહયોગી હનીફ ખોખરે.


વીડિયો- હનીફ ખોખર/ સુમિત વૈદ્ય

તમે અમારી સાથે જોડાઈ શકો છો :

snippet.title: Dark Reality of Indian Education System | Dhruv Rathee
snippet.description:
Get real-life skills to create a remarkable impact in software development and data science, Check Out:
https://www.scaler.com/?utm_source=brandedcontent&utm_medium=DhruvratheeDec&utm_campaign=brand_scaler_academy_brandedcontent_DhruvratheeDec_branded-content-video-campaign-DhruvratheeDec-08December2022_india_all&utm_content=YT-description

Aamir Khan's 3 idiots was a superhit movie back then in 2009. We all loved it, but it seems that the message is still not implemented. Because even today in 2022, the pressure on students to pursue stereotypical degrees like engineering, doctor, etc. is real. A kid has to convince his parents to allow him to do something like becoming a YouTuber, Graphic Designer, Video Editor, etc. But why the situation is like this? Why do we have such strong stereotypes? Watch this video by Dhruv Rathee as he explains the root cause of this unfortunate problem that continues to exist in our society for decades - the education system.

0:00 Introduction
1:59 Mass Media Conditioning 
5:11 Parents Influence 
10:26 Yourself / Cognitive Biases 
15:04 School infrastructure

en.title: Dark Reality of Indian Education System | Dhruv Rathee
en.description:
Get real-life skills to create a remarkable impact in software development and data science, Check Out:
https://www.scaler.com/?utm_source=brandedcontent&utm_medium=DhruvratheeDec&utm_campaign=brand_scaler_academy_brandedcontent_DhruvratheeDec_branded-content-video-campaign-DhruvratheeDec-08December2022_india_all&utm_content=YT-description

Aamir Khan's 3 idiots was a superhit movie back then in 2009. We all loved it, but it seems that the message is still not implemented. Because even today in 2022, the pressure on students to pursue stereotypical degrees like engineering, doctor, etc. is real. A kid has to convince his parents to allow him to do something like becoming a YouTuber, Graphic Designer, Video Editor, etc. But why the situation is like this? Why do we have such strong stereotypes? Watch this video by Dhruv Rathee as he explains the root cause of this unfortunate problem that continues to exist in our society for decades - the education system.

Time codes

0:00 Introduction
1:59 Mass Media Conditioning 
5:11 Parents Influence 
10:26 Yourself / Cognitive Biases 
15:04 School infrastructure
15:59 Teachers

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3637 - 9 Dec 2022 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3637
--------------------------------------------------------
Popatlal meets Vidya and then heads back to Gokhuldham. Bhide inquires about Popatlal's whereabouts because he has been absent from society. Popatlal tells Bhide that he was busy with a sting operation. Later, Bhide's uncle Sudhakar Ji calls him, and he sounds furious since he observed Popatlal meeting Vidya covertly. Bhide is shocked to learn that Popatlal had visited the village and met Vidya. He is puzzled and attempts to understand how Popatlal learned the location of the village and Vidya. Watch the episode.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3637, 9 Dec 2022
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab

https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.description:

Siyani Episode 117 - [Eng Sub] - Anmol Baloch - Mohsin Abbas Haider -Saniya Shamshad - 9th December 2022

Hailing from a lower-middle-class family, Kiran is a selfish and arrogant girl who aspires to achieve a lifestyle through mending her ways and taking shortcuts. Kiran’s mother Nusrat Ara is aware of her daughter’s nature and doesn’t stop her from doing anything. On the contrary, Ujala is a well-mannered and beautiful girl who lives with Kiran’s family and strives to become independent. 

Zarbab, a handsome young man who belongs to an influential and wealthy family. His first meeting with Kiran turns out to be magical as he falls in love at first sight. Kiran sees him as a way to advance forward in life and builds a web of lies and deceit around Zarbab. On the other hand, Ujala is forced to live a life deprived of love and unfulfilled dreams.

Will Ujala ever find the love and respect that she deserves? After building her life on lies and deception, how long will Kiran be able to conceal the truth?

Written By: Sadia Akhtar
Directed By: Ali Akbar
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Anmol Baloch - Kiran
Usama Khan - Zohaib
Saniya Shamshad - Ujala
Mohsin Abbas Haider - Zarbaab
Erum Akhter - Reema
Tipu Shareef - Bakhtiyar
Parveen Akbar - Fazeelat
Beena Chaudhary - Nusrat
Hashim Butt

UP Bypolls Results 2022: उत्तर प्रदेश में Mainpuri, Rampur और Khatauli की सीट पर उपचुनाव के नतीजे सामने आ गए हैं. रामपुर में बीजेपी और खतौली में सपा गठबंधन को जीत हासिल हुई है. वहीं Mainpuri लोकसभा सीट पर सपा की Dimple Yadav ने बड़े मार्जन से बीजेपी प्रत्याशी Raghuraj Singh Shakya को धूल चटा दी. उपचुनाव के नतीजे सामने आने के बाद प्रदेश के CM Yogi Adityanath ने डिंपल यादव को मैनपुरी सीट पर जीत की बधाई दी. साथ ही सीएम ने खतौली और रामपुर के विजेता प्रत्याशियों को भी जीत की शुभकामनाएं दी.

Lyrics -

Chhori tedhi tedhi taak ke,
Likdi saare mauke naap ke,
Chhora ke khanjar ghaal ke,
Beran dar ja kade ram te,

Chhori tedhi tedhi taak ke,
Likdi saare mauke naap ke,
Chhora ke khanjar ghaal ke,
Beran dar ja kade ram te,

Chhori Ghani syaani ghani syaani ghani syaani,
Chhore mar gaye mar gaye mar gaye haan bin maange paani,

Nakhro, dekha pahli dafa,
College ke bahar dass kya thi raza,
Chale left to right bata kyu di saza,
Louis, LV tight teri kaidi ada,
Chhore paache paache haande leke landi jeep,
Tere chakkar me kare kaand galt hi cheej,
Gere 5 inch heel, Chhore leve poori feel,
Tere bhaav bhi to fly kare poori dheel,

Makke tip to toe tu poori gach hai,
26 ki kamar poori lachke,
21 ki umar, kya ye sach hai?
Mere bethi hai nishaane pe rah bachke,

Halla mach gaya poore gaam me,
Ib bethak laage shaam ne,
Chhora ke khanjar ghaal ke,
Beran darja kadi raam te,

Chhori Ghani syaani ghani syaani ghani syaani,
Chhore mar gaye mar gaye mar gaye haan bin maange paani,

Tu hoga badmaash tere laake me chhore,
Tere jaise pade fail mere khaate me chhore,
Manne Jhaanse me laane ki koshish na kar,
Maanja padega ghane ghaate me chhore,

Teri chikni chupdi baat me,
Chhori aati koni saath me,
Chhora ke khanjar ghaal ke,
Kyunkar darjua raam te,

Haan me ghani syaani ghani syaani ghani syaani,
Chhore mar gaye mar gaye mar gaye haan bin maange paani


#GhaniSyaani #MCSquare #ShehnaazGill

About MaaTri Media

MaaTri, represents the most beautiful relationship between a mother and a daughter - Nisha Topwal & Anantya Anand aka. MyMissAnand.

MaaTri is formed through a combination of two Hindi words - Maa (Mother) and PuTri (daughter) that brings forth energy, enthusiasm and determination to spread positive vibes through their outstanding content. Their content revolves around fashion, food, comedy, parenting, travel, glimpse of their family and simple day-to-day activities that both enjoy doing together. 
The duo captures a contemporary lifestyle of entrepreneur and food blogger mom and a teenage daughter and a social media influencer and shows how they both manage their work, school and personal life - simple pleasure of growing together, through engaging videos and fun visuals. Every post is curated and designed to make the audience laugh, learn, smile and entertain. 

Watch our videos every Thursday & learn new dishes and kitchen hacks or food hacks with us as we entertain you with our comical presentation.

snippet.title: Realme 10 Pro+ Unboxing & First Look - The Ultimate Midrange Phone🔥🔥🔥
snippet.description:
Namaskaar Dosto, is video mein maine aapse baat ki hai Realme 10 Pro+ ke baare mein aur yaha pe maine aapse share ki hai Realme 10 Pro+ ki unboxing, aur kuch details yaha pe isi Realme 10 Pro+ ke baare mein. Realme 10 Pro+ mein 6.7" FHD+ Curved Super AMOLED Display hai Punch Hole Design ke saath jaha pe hai 120Hz Refresh Rate saath hi isme hai MediaTek Dimensity 1080 Octa Core 5G Processor saath mein hai 6GB/8GB RAM aur 128GB ki Internal Storage. Realme 10 Pro+ mein Triple Rear camera setup 108MP Primary + 8MP Ultrawide + 2MP Ultra Macro ke saath, aur saath mein 16MP ka front facing Selfie camera hai. Realme 9 Pro+ mein 5000mAh ki battery hai 67W Flash Charger ke saath mein. Mujhe umeed hai ki aapko Realme 10 Pro+ ki yeh Unboxing aur First Look video pasand aayegi. 

Realme 10 Pro+ Price in India:
6GB+128GB = 24,999INR
8GB+128GB = 25,999INR

#Realme10Series #Realme10Pro+ #TechnicalGuruji
